{
  "name": "RPlog_Terror_on_Tatooine",
  "title": "Survival in Beggar's Canyon",
  "summary": "In Beggar's Canyon on Tatooine, the scarred and hate-filled Morganna, who has secretly been sent to kill her companion Avid, is caught with him when a savage Tusken Raider war band closes in. Forced to flee into a deadly sandstorm rather than fight twenty-to-two, the pair are flayed by driving sand until Morganna stumbles upon a small cave. As they take shelter, a lone Tusken youth braves the storm and wounds Avid badly across the back before he kills it, leaving him unconscious and at Morganna's mercy; she raises his own vibroblade to murder him but cannot bring herself to finish the strike. Trapped, terrified by the closing dark, and reduced to a vulnerable, childlike state, Morganna instead helps tend Avid's wounds, and he comforts her tenderly through the long night, vowing she will never be a slave again. When the storm finally passes and they dig free, the exhausted Avid carries the injured Morganna across the burning dunes toward Mos Eisley, sharing the last of their water, until a passing speeder driver stops and agrees to take the dying pair to safety.",
